  "title": "Site Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Support site planning, coordination and daily operations</li><li>Monitor work progress, technical quality and safety compliance</li><li>Work closely with subcontractors, consultants and site teams</li><li>Assist in resolving technical/site issues and provide practical solutions</li><li>Prepare and maintain site reports, records and documentation</li><li>Ensure works follow drawings, specifications and construction standards</li><li>Coordinate materials, manpower and work sequencing</li><li>Able to work independently, handle fast-paced site conditions</li><li>Good communication, problem-solving and basic computer skills</li><li>Relevant site/engineering experience preferred</li></ul>",
